58.5	Threads	Threads	Threads is a British television drama produced by the BBC in 1984. Written by Barry Hines and directed by Mick Jackson, it is a documentary-style account of a nuclear war and its effects on the city of Sheffield in northern England.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/3/35/Threadsmoviecover.jpg/220px-Threadsmoviecover.jpg
